name: Add for UK Special Delivery
description:
Add to your cart if you would like your order to be sent by Special Delivery (UK only).  This price is in addition to the standard postage charge added at checkout.  Please note this does not prioritise your order but simply upgrade the service by which it is sent.

Orders sent by this method will be provided with a tracking number and are guaranteed to arrive by 1pm on the next working day following dispatch (excludes Saturdays).  A signature will be required upon delivery.

name: Add for International Signed-For
description:
Add to your cart if you would like your order to be sent by International Signed-For service.  This price is in addition to the standard postage charge of £4.00 added to your total at checkout.  Please note this does not prioritise your order but simply upgrade the service by which it is sent.
